---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Divorce Lawyer for Professionals in Maryland | Divorce With A Plan"
  description="Maryland divorce attorneys for doctors, lawyers, executives, and high-earning professionals. Protecting professional licenses, complex income, and business interests during divorce."
  ogTitle="Divorce Lawyer for Professionals in Maryland | Divorce With A Plan"
  ogDescription="Specialized divorce representation for Maryland professionals. We protect your career, income, and assets. Rockville & Baltimore offices. Free consultation."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-700 text-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Divorce Lawyers for Maryland Professionals</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Divorce Representation Built<br class="hidden md:block" />
        for High-Achieving Professionals
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Doctors, attorneys, executives, and other professionals face unique divorce challenges that generic family law firms aren't equipped to handle. Our Maryland attorneys understand the intersection of professional success and divorce law.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/free-consultation" class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Schedule Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="tel:2402693592" class="border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Call (240) 269-3592
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Professionals Need Specialized Counsel -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5">Why Professionals Need Specialized Divorce Counsel</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            If you're a high-earning professional, your divorce involves complexities that most divorce attorneys rarely encounter. <strong>Variable income, deferred compensation, professional licenses, practice ownership, and stock options</strong> all require specialized legal and financial analysis.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            A misstep in how your income is calculated can dramatically affect spousal support and child support obligations. An error in how your professional practice is valued could cost you hundreds of thousands of dollars.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            At Divorce With A Plan, we have experience handling the financial complexity that comes with professional-level divorces — and we partner with forensic accountants and business valuators to ensure every number is defensible.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Unique Challenges for Professionals</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              "Complex, variable, or deferred compensation structures",
              "Professional practice valuation disputes",
              "Professional license — marital vs. separate property",
              "Stock options, RSUs, and equity compensation",
              "Goodwill (personal vs. enterprise) in professional practices",
              "Partnership and shareholder agreement conflicts",
              "Retirement plans unique to professional employment",
              "Protecting professional reputation and privacy"
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-sm">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Professionals We Serve -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Professionals We Represent</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We serve a wide range of professionals throughout Maryland who need sophisticated, discreet divorce representation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { icon: "🏥", title: "Physicians & Surgeons", desc: "Medical practices, hospital employment contracts, and physician income structures require specialized analysis." },
          { icon: "⚖️", title: "Attorneys & Judges", desc: "Legal professionals understand the stakes — and need attorneys who can handle the unique aspects of legal practice ownership." },
          { icon: "🏢", title: "Corporate Executives", desc: "Base salary, bonuses, stock options, RSUs, and deferred compensation all factor into Maryland divorce proceedings." },
          { icon: "🦷", title: "Dentists & Healthcare Providers", desc: "Healthcare practice valuations and professional goodwill issues are handled with precision." },
          { icon: "💰", title: "Financial Professionals", desc: "Bankers, investment advisors, and financial executives often have complex compensation and equity structures." },
          { icon: "🔬", title: "Engineers & Scientists", desc: "Technical professionals with intellectual property rights, patents, and equity compensation need specialized counsel." }
        ].map(pro => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">{pro.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">{pro.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">{pro.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Income Calculation Issues -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Income Calculation: More Than Just Your Salary</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">For professionals, "income" in a Maryland divorce context is far more complex than your W-2. Getting this calculation right — or wrong — can have major long-term financial consequences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Income Sources Courts May Consider</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            {[
              "Base salary and wages",
              "Bonuses and performance incentives",
              "Self-employment and business income",
              "Partnership distributions",
              "Deferred compensation payments",
              "Stock option exercises",
              "Investment and dividend income",
              "Rental income from properties",
              "Expense reimbursements that reduce personal costs"
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-amber-500 text-sm mt-1">•</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why This Matters for You</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">Spousal support (alimony) and child support in Maryland are both calculated based on income. If your income is incorrectly inflated — or if your spouse's income is understated — the resulting support obligations may be unfair.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">Our attorneys work with financial experts to <strong>accurately document and present your income</strong> to the court, accounting for fluctuations, deferrals, and non-cash compensation.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">We also know how to identify when a spouse is concealing or underreporting income — a common tactic in professional divorce cases.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Professional Goodwill -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Personal Goodwill vs. Enterprise Goodwill</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
            In Maryland, <strong>enterprise goodwill</strong> (the value of the business independent of the owner) may be subject to division as marital property. However, <strong>personal goodwill</strong> — the value tied to an individual's reputation, skills, and relationships — is generally not.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            This distinction is critically important for physicians, attorneys, dentists, and other licensed professionals whose practice value is closely tied to their personal reputation. We work with professional appraisers to properly separate and argue these components.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5">Protecting Your Professional Practice</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            Your professional practice may be the most valuable asset in your divorce — and also the most complicated to address. Whether you're a solo practitioner or a partner in a large firm, we understand how professional practice valuation works under Maryland law.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            We work proactively to <strong>limit the marital portion of your practice's value</strong>, properly classify personal goodwill, and structure a resolution that allows your practice to continue operating without disruption.
          </p>
          <a href="/divorces-involving-businesses" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-semibold text-sm">
            Learn more about business divorce cases →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy & Discretion -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Discretion is Our Standard</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        For professionals, the public nature of divorce proceedings can create professional and reputational risks. Josephia Rouse and her team are known for handling sensitive matters with exceptional discretion. We explore every option for privacy protection — including collaborative divorce and private mediation — while never compromising your legal position.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { title: "Confidential Consultations", desc: "Every consultation is fully confidential under attorney-client privilege." },
          { title: "Strategic Privacy Protection", desc: "We explore mediation and collaborative divorce to keep sensitive matters out of public court records." },
          { title: "Professional Network", desc: "We work with financial experts and forensic accountants who understand the confidentiality requirements of professional divorce cases." }
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-400 mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-amber-500">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Your Career and Assets Deserve Expert Protection</h2>
      <p class="text-amber-100 mb-8 text-lg">Schedule a confidential consultation with our Maryland divorce attorneys for professionals.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/free-consultation" class="bg-white text-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-50 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Book Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="tel:2402693592" class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-amber-600 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          (240) 269-3592
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
